text: Dana Procházková is an orienteering competitor who competed for Czechoslovakia. At the 1974 World Orienteering Championships in Viborg she won a bronze medal in the relay, together with Anna Handzlová and Renata Vlachová. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Czechoslovak orienteers Category:Female orienteers Category:Foot orienteers Category:World Orienteering Championships medalists
